        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The best places to find words on vendors is in places where nobody will be able to use them.  For example, no "good" race will use 99% of the words for necro spells, so you should begin to check out towns near areas where the proper level mobs are.  Offhand I'm thinking Firiona Vie docks might be the best place to search vendors for your current level words.  Just start a level 1 lighty bard mule and use him to run around to find stuff, with invis and selo's you can get almost anywhere.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
